# 🌐 🔐 Accounts (Login / User)

```text id="api_acc"
POST /api/accounts/register/     → Benutzer registrieren
POST /api/accounts/login/        → JWT Login (access + refresh)
POST /api/accounts/refresh/      → neuen access Token holen
GET  /api/accounts/me/           → aktueller eingeloggter User
```

---

# 👤 Customers

```text id="api_cus"
GET    /api/customers/           → alle Kunden
POST   /api/customers/           → neuen Kunden erstellen
GET    /api/customers/{id}/      → einzelner Kunde
PUT    /api/customers/{id}/      → Kunde bearbeiten
PATCH  /api/customers/{id}/      → teilweise ändern
DELETE /api/customers/{id}/      → Kunde löschen
```

